title: O'Neill Evolution 2011 - Halfpipe Women Finals
description: Kelly Clark dominates the Halfpipe Women Finals during the O'Neill Evolution 2011. In second 19 year old Slovenian rider Cilka Sadar and third Norwegian rider Kjersti Ostgaard Buaas.
